info.name: Tumblr | Cabin Pressure Dashboard Icons
info.description: Cabin Pressure-inspired icons for the new tumblr dashboard setup. Plane (dashboard), lemon (inbox), cheese (help), bear polar (settings).
info.additionalInfo: icarusing.tumblr.com (Note: Preview includes the missing e logo, which will only show up for users of missing e and isn't included in this script. Logout logo is unchanged but may be in the future.) Thanks to kriegzhan for the inspiration!
